From 0ccc2f3d85960b5886fa100baccec0a57881d8d4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Work Leaf Bench <bench@example.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:04:46 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] ADD selected-agent slash commands for backend status
 workflows

Selected chat messages that begin with a slash command now execute through the agent backend command surface instead of being sent as ordinary prompts. Codex implements /status and /fork from recorded session state so users can inspect or fork the selected session without resuming it with command text.
